				<a>
					<img src="assets/mainpage/NetflixDramas.png" />
				</a>
			</Column>
		</Row>
		<div class="bigDivider"></div>
		<h2>Join the Conversation!</h2>
		<div class="mainYellowDivider"></div>
		<div class="blankDivider"></div>
		<!--Conversation Block-->
		<Row>
			<Column ColumnSize = "ColumnSize.Is5">
				<img style="height: 280px;" src="assets/mainpage/Find_Yourself_Waterview.jpg" />
			</Column>
			<Column ColumnSize="ColumnSize.Is5">
				<h3>TRAVEL TO CHINA</h3>
				<h4>Locations from the biggest year in C-Drama</h4>
				<p>
					The infamous Korean game neolttwigi played by Queen Cheorin (Shin Hye-sun).
					<br /><br />
					Better known as a traditional outdoor game of Korean women and girls that
					is typically enjoyed on traditional holidays, neolttwigi is typically
					enjoyed on traditional holidays such as Korean New Year, Chuseok, and Dano.
					Neolttwigi is similar to seesaw, except that participants stand on each end
					of the Neol and jump, propelling the person opposite into the air.
				</p>
			</Column>
		</Row>
		<div class="bigDivider"></div>
		<h2>The World of Hayao Miyazaki</h2>
		<div class="mainYellowDivider"></div>
		<div class="blankDivider"></div>
